data.description: Well established neighborhood with 2 community pools, tennis courts and a playground.  Home has great curb appeal and has been well maintained.  Living area has wood beamed cathedral ceiling, wood burning fireplace and a wet bar.  Wood paneled study or could be a theater room, a play room or nursery connecting to primary bedroom. Large kitchen with beautiful solid wood cabinets, built in desk, large pantry and dinette area.  Spacious formal dining or formal living area with a bay window.  Utility room as a sink and extra storage.  All bedrooms are large in size.  Primary bedroom has a large walk in closet and a door that leads out to patio to enjoy the newer hot tub.  All new light fixtures, windows 2019, interior paint and cabinet hardware.  Home is in great condition.  Make your appointment today!
